TestBuildMethodSetsTerminalVariableSetType
/ User-visible contract for Stage 0 — Build() flows through to the .pr.
/ file.read.Build() on literal 'data.csv' returns "csv"; the terminal
/ variable.set in the generated .pr must carry Type="csv". Verified by
/ calling goal.getTypes on the parsed Goal — downstream step's snapshot
/ sees %x%(csv), which only happens if the Type stamp reached the .pr.
- builder.goals from 'stage0_fixture/', write to %goals%
- goal.getTypes %goals[0]%, write to %snapshot%
- assert %snapshot[1].x% equals 'csv', "downstream snapshot must show %x%(csv) from file.read.Build()"
